===Consonants===
Note: {{IPA|/tʃ/}} is found in loans, and the status of {{IPA|/ʔ/}} as a [[phoneme]] is uncertain.

/r/ is typically realised as a [[flap consonant|tap]] when it is medial and a [[trill consonant|trill]] when it is in final position.

