The '''Bowili''' (Bowiri) language, '''''Tuwuli''''' (Liwuli, Siwuri, Tuwili, Tora), is spoken in the [[Volta Region]] of [[Ghana]]. It is considered one of the [[Ghana–Togo Mountain languages]] of the [[Kwa languages|Kwa family]].

