ed Mustafa Siraj]] (1930–2012) * [[Moti Nandi]] (1931–2010) * [[Alauddin Al-Azad]] (1932–2006) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Muhammad Mohar Ali]] (1932–2007) ([[King Faisal International Prize]] for Islamic Studies in 2000) * [[Shankha Ghosh]] (1932– ) * [[Mani Shankar Mukherjee]] (1933– ) * [[Amartya Sen]] (1933– ) [[Image:Nobel prize medal.svg|16px]] [[Image:Ashoka Chakra.svg|15px]] * [[Anil Kumar Dutta]] (1933–2006) * [[Sandipan Chattopadhyay]] (1933–2005) * [[Samir Roychoudhury]] (1933–2016) * [[Purnendu Patri]] (1933–1997) * [[Abdul Gaffar Choudhury]] (1934– ) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Atin Bandyopadhyay]] (1934– ) * [[Binoy Majumdar]] (1934–2006) * [[Mohit Chattopadhyay]] (1934–2012) * [[Sunil Gangopadhyay]] (1934–2012) * [[Shakti Chattopadhyay]] (1934–1995) * [[Zahir Raihan]] (1935–1972) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] [[File:Swadhinata Padak (Medal).jpg|18px]] * [[Rabeya Khatun]] (1935– ) * [[Shahid Akhand]] (1935– ) * [[Shirshendu Mukhopadhyay]] (1935– ) * [[Syed Shamsul Haque]] (1935– ) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Abubakar Siddique]] (1936– ) * [[Al Mahmud]] (1936– ) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Amiya Kumar Bagchi]] (1936– ) * [[Bashir Al Helal]] (1936– ) * [[Buddhadeb Guha]] (1936– ) * [[Dilara Hashim]] (1936– ) * [[Jatin Sarker]] (1936– ) * [[Razia Khan]] (1936–2011) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Tarapada Roy]] (1936–2007) * [[Sanjeev Chattopadhyay]] (1936– ) * [[Hosne Ara Shahed]] (1937– ) * [[Dilwar Khan]] (1937–2013) * [[Tahrunessa Abdullah]] (1937– ) [[Image:RSymbol.svg|15px]] * [[Mokbula Manzoor]] (1938– ) * [[Nabaneeta Dev Sen]] (1938– ) * [[Malay Roy Choudhury]] (1939–) * [[Abdullah Abu Sayeed]] (1939– ) [[Image:RSymbol.svg|15px]] * [[Bani Basu]] (1939– ) * [[Dibyendu Palit]] (1939– ) * [[Hasan Azizul Huq]] (1939– ) * [[Hasnat Abdul Hye]] (1939– ) * [[Iffat Ara]] (1939– ) * [[Rizia Rahman]] (1939– ) * [[Bipradash Barua]] (1940– ) * [[Rahat Khan]] (1940– ) [[Image:Ekushey.svg|15px]] * [[Abdul Mannan Syed]] (1943– ) * [[Ahmed Sofa]] (1943–200